snippet.textDisplay: I've said this before and I'll say it again - Jisung really reminds me of Taemin in so many ways. They both debuted at the super young age of 14. They're both the shy, yet super charismatic maknaes of their group. They dance seemingly effortlessly, yet with so much passion, and a similar dance style, at that. Just like Taemin blew the world away with his matured talent in his solo debut, I feel that in the future, Jisung will do the same and we won't be able to handle it. He's a legend in the making, if you will. I don't know if I'm the only one who sees this in these two, but I really think there are many uncanny similarities. I really love them and I'm living for their interactions! üíï
